1
00:00:00,001 --> 00:00:07,161
Armenians are distinguished by performing
their prayers and rituals in Armenian

2
00:00:07,186 --> 00:00:10,521
In addition, the clothing worn by the priest is different

3
00:00:10,547 --> 00:00:16,562
Through the rituals and masses he performs

4
00:00:16,587 --> 00:00:21,380
His attire differs from the clothing that is
normally worn

5
00:00:21,405 --> 00:00:23,802
By Christian priests outside Armenian churches

6
00:00:23,854 --> 00:00:28,281
In addition to many special feast days

7
00:00:28,306 --> 00:00:30,182
For saints, as I mentioned

8
00:00:30,207 --> 00:00:32,396
These do not exist in non-Armenian churches

9
00:00:32,421 --> 00:00:36,094
Such as Etchmiadzin and Saint Gregory

10
00:00:36,119 --> 00:00:38,958
And many of those saints

11
00:00:38,983 --> 00:00:41,849
Are designated specifically in the Armenian Church
